{"tid":1006231,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"低調高手大街小食既格仔餅 雞蛋仔係香港算幾高質？","createTime":"2019-02-02T20:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T21:13:56.000Z","uid":221748,"like":10,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8c0692c9d1770bba6a3d111f42a5c41289d115fc","tid":1006231,"uid":221748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T20:15:51.000Z","msg":"格仔餅 雞蛋仔都好鬆脆 有蛋香 又唔會比空心雞蛋仔你<br />\n仲有好重要既係佢即叫即整 其實只要係即叫即整都唔會差得去邊 不過好多店都整定 搞到佢出名 <br />\n不過老老實實佢唔係用炭燒 一定去唔到最高境界<br />\n而且佢太多人排 有時要成半個鐘先有 又偏貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要d明星效應都吸引好多人 JJ Edson 都食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搞到我宜家就算住得近都少食左 因為太多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mocPyTM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmocPyTM.png&h=8a8f4617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw我有寫下食評 大家可以follow下 宜家返左英國 好快有英國post睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇下我點係屎中搵到黃金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=b6tys16aweok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ffoodkiller_dk%3Futm_source%3Dig_profile_share%26igshid%3Db6tys16aweok&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7hjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=8c8a02f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=b6tys16aweok</a>"},{"pid":"bb052dd371ba452a4e7d93506bf207a3453aa091","tid":1006231,"uid":59665,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T20:26:46.000Z","msg":"好多年前食過一次覺得好好食 <br />\n上年有日放假經過買黎食 空心既屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從此就無再食過"},{"pid":"1cb19d2e6dde480497678a0409ea246892d9abf5","tid":1006231,"uid":221748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"q